Direct Known Subclasses:
GraphRequest, MultiqueryRequest
public abstract class GraphRequestBase<T>
extends Request<T>

Common behavior for the requests that get batched at the top level.

A little trick: This object is also serialized out to JSON as the array of batch parameters to the Facebook call. Its getters return the appropriate data.
